  Hit-tiap8 gin2-na2 lau7-lang5 long2 kui7-teh. Li7-su-te7 chai Chu2 li7 i bo5 hng7, chiu7 ki5-to2 kong2, "Chu2 Ia5-sou ah! Tok-hui kap goa2 lai5 kau3 li2 bin7-cheng5, goan2 tai7-ke u7 loa7-che7 e5 choe7, si7 eng-kai tioh8 se2-khi3, thoan5-to7-e5 iah8 u7 kong2, li2 bo5 beh chiong goan2 tai7-ke koaN2--chhut-khi3; te5-bak8 sou2 kong2, si7 it-khai3 e5 choe7; taN siuN7 goa2 kap Tok-hui e5 choe7, iah8 sng3 chai7-lai7. Kiu5 Chu2 eng7 po2-hoeh se2 goan2 e5 sim, se2 kau3 peh8-peh8, goan2 kam-goan7 hoaN-hi2 kau3 An-lok8-ke, si7 sim sou2 goan7." 
  Tok-hui toe3 Li7-su-te7 kong2, "Kiu5 Chu2 se2 goan2 nng7 e5 lang5, piN3-chiaN5 peh8-peh8 e5 seh, chhiaN2 li2 khan--goan2, kiu3--goan2, sim sou2 goan7." 
  Tui3 hit-tiap8 nng7 lang5 khia7--khi2-lai5. Li7-su-te7 tui3 Tok-hui kong2, "Lan2 lai5 khi3 khun3, sou2 ki5-kiu5-e5 Chu2 i2-keng thiaN-kiN3 lah." 
